{"tid":555422,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人因為自己性格問題而錯過咗好多人？","createTime":"2018-02-09T12:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-10T16:49:44.000Z","uid":6219,"like":116,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"40377e35ede3780efe99408f2ec7df826a5b023d","tid":555422,"uid":6219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"自己性格上都玩得 講得笑 咩都可以傾 但係因為份人慢熱 怕得罪人 同介意人地點睇自己 所以識新朋友 同事都會好被動 唔知點開話題好 人地明明好熱情都因為咁而唔想再同自己交流 自己都試過主動啲 講下笑 但係覺得好假 同好唔自在 感覺上一定要識耐左先可以同對方傾得放啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見到啲人性格應該同自己夾得黎 甚至做到好朋友 但係因為咁嘅性格令對方冇咩興趣同你深交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好羨慕啲人同對方識左冇耐就可以攬頭攬頸 周圍去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦都係因為呢種性格搞到冇咩朋友 所以自己好珍惜而家嘅朋友 好驚冇左佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fe1640cf1ec10a7d5858a1a221f198d2a746af","tid":555422,"uid":85564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:03:40.000Z","msg":"same here <br />\n<br />\ntake it slow<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32141198922e79225213fd078e91d7419a11fef","tid":555422,"uid":160237,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 但睇開左 唔強求"},{"pid":"e57d023fa0cca47f096748ca1e79492692e0bfcc","tid":555422,"uid":80836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:06:14.000Z","msg":"做咩寫我啲感受出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db5920ff2377699f16e4345fd35f14b44b348ed","tid":555422,"uid":75719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"錯過咗太多人 依家一個講到心事既朋友都冇<br />\n其實都唔緊要 習慣哂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f4f5cb40e1fe0912a404db08bc8a92eef89c0d1","tid":555422,"uid":104213,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-09T1